00:36:00,613 --> 00:36:04,625
So you guys disappeared because you did it?

494
00:36:06,044 --> 00:36:07,331
The fridge is mine.

495
00:36:08,223 --> 00:36:09,776
It’s for my luxurious drinks.

496
00:36:10,649 --> 00:36:13,524
And I got the seat in the back.

497
00:36:13,687 --> 00:36:15,088
Freaking comfy.

498
00:36:15,088 --> 00:36:17,032
Since we’re all here,

499
00:36:17,295 --> 00:36:19,260
I have a gift for our new studio.

500
00:36:19,260 --> 00:36:19,773
What?

501
00:36:19,773 --> 00:36:20,393
What is it?

502
00:36:20,553 --> 00:36:21,359
