503
00:36:24,228 --> 00:36:25,352
What do you think it is?

504
00:36:26,300 --> 00:36:27,461
Something expensive.

505
00:36:29,852 --> 00:36:30,831
I can’t wait.

506
00:36:33,390 --> 00:36:36,552
In a note from the tree planting class I took,

507
00:36:36,797 --> 00:36:39,462
