508
00:36:39,698 --> 00:36:40,751
A Pink Trumpet tree.

509
00:36:43,025 --> 00:36:43,902
Hold on, Tun.

510
00:36:44,808 --> 00:36:49,922
How big is a Pink Trumpet tree when it’s fully grown?

511
00:36:50,033 --> 00:36:52,672
Around 8-25 meters.

512
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:54,171
Wait.

513
00:36:54,836 --> 00:36:57,392
Are you planting a 25-meter-tall tree in an RV?

514
00:36:58,245 --> 00:36:59,116
Are you kidding?

515
00:36:59,641 --> 00:37:01,225
Well, trim it.

516
00:37:01,498 --> 00:37:05,952
Besides, won’t you be happy to wake up and see a pretty pink tree?

517
00:37:06,967 --> 00:37:07,671
No.

518
00:37:08,213 --> 00:37:09,432
I don’t think pink.

519
00:37:10,197 --> 00:37:11,777
But its meaning is very nice.

520
00:37:11,972 --> 00:37:14,392
It represents love and good wishes.

521
00:37:14,512 --> 00:37:16,774
It fits romantic film screenwriters like us.

522
00:37:17,981 --> 00:37:18,881
That’s true.

523
00:37:19,143 --> 00:37:19,745
Aou.

524
00:37:19,745 --> 00:37:20,245
What?

525
00:37:20,328 --> 00:37:22,066
Let’s make room for our amulet.

526
00:37:23,476 --> 00:37:24,811
Where should we place it?

