00:38:26,129 --> 00:38:27,792
Glad I got to use it today.

546
00:38:27,926 --> 00:38:29,384
Get closer.

547
00:38:29,513 --> 00:38:31,810
Tess, closer. You don’t want to be out of the frame.

548
00:38:31,950 --> 00:38:32,498
Sure.

549
00:38:34,096 --> 00:38:36,096
In the end, they fall in love with each other.

550
00:38:37,743 --> 00:38:38,274
What?

551
00:38:48,906 --> 00:38:51,256
Will you spend tonight with me?

552
00:38:51,433 --> 00:38:54,352
There are many things I want to do before I die.

553
00:38:54,650 --> 00:38:55,950
But now

554
00:38:57,179 --> 00:38:59,319
there’s one thing I want to do the most.

555
00:39:57,465 --> 00:39:58,689
Yes, Dol?

556
00:39:59,355 --> 00:40:00,131
What?

557
00:40:01,059 --> 00:40:03,648
A guide video for new universal travelers?

558
00:40:03,775 --> 00:40:04,759
Yes.

559
00:40:04,759 --> 00:40:09,795
Do you see there’re lots of new travelers here?

